## 🧩 BONUS IDEA

Mix 3 formats to grow faster:

* Face-based **daily short explainers (1–2 min)**
* Face + screen **detailed circulars (5–7 min)**
* Face-only **career talk (3–4 min)**

That gives both **CTR** (shorts) and **Watch Time** (longs).

